OL,3,CGirl, 13, to appear in court over
OL,4,Calleged stabbing at school
OL,6,FThe 13-year-old, who cannot be named,
OL,7,Fwas remanded in custody to appear
OL,8,Fbefore Llanelli Magistrates' Court.
OL,10,FMichael Cray, senior Crown prosecutor
OL,11,Fat CPS Cymru-Wales, said the girl had
OL,12,Fbeen charged with three counts of
OL,13,Fattempted murder and possession of a
OL,14,Fbladed article on a school premises.
OL,16,F"Criminal proceedings are active and
OL,17,Fthe defendant has the right to a fair
OL,18,Ftrial," he added.
