OL,3,CGirl, 13, to appear in court over
OL,4,Calleged stabbing at school
OL,6,FThe West Wales school went into
OL,7,Flockdown after a "code red" alarm
OL,8,Fsounded through the PA system, during
OL,9,Fwhich students and staff are said to
OL,10,Fhave hidden in classrooms.
OL,12,FThe lockdown lasted around four hours
OL,13,Fbetween 11.20am and 3.20pm, resulting
OL,14,Fin a lengthy and anxious wait for
OL,15,Fparents who were seen tearfully
OL,16,Fhugging their children after they
OL,17,Fwalked through the gates.
